        "id": "comment-intro",
        "parent_id": null,
        "type": "nodetool.workflows.base_node.Comment",
        "data": {
          "comment": "# 🔒 Private Assistant\n\nA fully local Q&A assistant. Paste your own notes, ask a question, and a local **Ollama** model answers — grounded only in your text. No API key, no cloud call: the document never leaves your machine.\n\n**Pipeline:** Document + question + tone → prompt template → local Ollama agent (answers only from the document) → Markdown answer.\n\n**Setup:** install [Ollama](https://ollama.com), then `ollama pull llama3.2`. Swap the model on the agent node for anything you have pulled (qwen2.5, gemma3, gpt-oss, …).\n\n**Try this:** paste a real doc into the Document input and ask something only it can answer — the assistant refuses to guess beyond the text."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "selected": false,
          "position": {
            "x": 60,
            "y": -240
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 560,
          "height": 240,
