        "data": {
          "name": "document",
          "value": "Team sync — Thursday\n- Launch date moved to March 14 (was March 7) to finish the accessibility fixes.\n- Priya owns the onboarding rewrite; first draft due Monday.\n- Budget: $8k left for Q1, reserved for the usability study.\n- Open risk: the billing migration hasn't been tested on staging yet.\n- Decision: ship the mobile app in the second wave, not at launch.",
          "description": "The private text the assistant may read — meeting notes, a doc, an email thread. This is the ONLY source the model is allowed to answer from; nothing is sent to the cloud."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
